title: Wonder Woman Unbound - Tim Hanley - EPUB
description:
Wonder Woman Unbound: The Curious History of the Worlds Most Famous Heroine
By Tim Hanley
2014
EPUB


This close look at Wonder Womans history portrays a complicated heroine who is more than just a female Superman with a golden lasso and bullet-deflecting bracelets.

The original Wonder Woman was ahead of her time, advocating female superiority and the benefits of matriarchy in the 1940s.
